desc: Sticks Corals is here to provide you with high end saltwater corals and Frags for your home reef aquarium. We carry a large selection of sps and lps varieties . While we try and aquaculture mostly unique varieties we also grow all your tried and true favorites of Chalices , favias, lps, sps ,anemones and mushrooms.

layout.text: Welcome to Sticks Corals where creating your dream Saltwater Reefs come true! What started out as a scuba diving trip yrs ago, resulted in acquiring our first saltwater tank as a way to bring a little piece of the ocean into our home. It has since escalated into a passion for reef tanks and growing aquacultured corals.
